org.influxdata.flux.functions

Class MeanFlux

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.influxdata.flux.Flux
      • org.influxdata.flux.functions.AbstractParametrizedFlux
        • org.influxdata.flux.functions.MeanFlux

  • public final class MeanFlux
extends AbstractParametrizedFlux
    Returns the mean of the within the results. See SPEC.

    Options

    • useStartTime - Use the start time as the timestamp of the resulting aggregate [boolean]

    Example

     Flux flux = Flux
     .from("telegraf")
     .range(-12L, ChronoUnit.HOURS)
     .window(10L, ChronoUnit.MINUTES)
     .mean();
    Author:
    Jakub Bednar (bednar@github) (25/06/2018 09:55)
